text.tspan: Preparation: In this stage, the person generally decides to
start to gather information about various resources. In
short, the person is testing water before diving in. Those in
this stage are generally taking small steps towards a
change but still they are hanging in the middle, because
those changes have not worked as they intended them to
be. For example, you know about various plans for de-
addiction, but you have never joined or actively participated
